umping factor, escape fraction, and spectral energy\ndistribution, we find that the $z\\sim6$ undetected galaxies down to z_850=30\nmag could have driven cosmic reionization.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Apr 2013 20:01:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
